<h2 id="which-tier">Which Tier Do You Actually Need?</h2>

<div class="callout callout-green">
  <strong>Single location, testing GHL:</strong> Start with the 30-day free trial, then Starter at $97/mo. Upgrade to Agency Unlimited when you add a second location or want Snapshots.
</div>

<div class="callout callout-blue">
  <strong>Multi-location operator (3+ locations):</strong> Go directly to Agency Unlimited at $297/mo. The per-location economics improve with every location you add. Starter's single-account limit makes it a dead end for operators.
</div>

<div class="callout callout-orange">
  <strong>Agency reselling GHL:</strong> SaaS Pro at $497/mo only if you're white-labeling GHL as your own product and charging clients. Otherwise, Agency Unlimited has everything.
</div>

